# ascist

For individuals who want to align long-term goals with weekly and daily chores, build a planning system so they can document six-month objectives, break them into weekly tasks, and execute them with confidence.

---

## Users & Value

- **Primary user / persona:** Young, ambitious Brazilians who completed the Imersão Ascensão weekend and want a digital companion for Augusto Weber’s Método Ascensão de Gestão de Tempo.
- **Jobs-to-be-done (JTBD):**
  - When I already have meus grandes objetivos de vida definidos após a imersão, I want an interface to break them into pequenas tarefas diárias so I can acompanhar o progresso constantemente.
  - When I defino objetivos e tarefas em cada Farol, I want to distribuir tudo na agenda semanal and exportar para o Google Calendar (sobrescrevendo versões anteriores) so I can executar o plano sem fricção.

---

## Success Metrics

- **Primary Goal:** Users arrange their weekly schedule with one-hour slots, color-coded Faróis, and sync their plan to Google Calendar.
- **Success Criteria:** TBD – no quantitative metric defined yet.

